Table oms.FinanceController2PaymentDefDO

Naming of finance controllers (debtor management systems) that can be used instead of defaults.

Columns 

References[1] Column Type Constraints[2] Default Comment
id integer PK, UNIQUE, NOT_NULL  
FinanceControllerDO financeControllerRef integer The finance controller the name should be used for. 
financeControllerPaymentExportName varchar(50) NOT_NULL The name of the payment method used for exports to the finance controller. Used for export of open amounts, sales order or purchase orders. Example "PayPal" 
financeControllerPaymentImportName varchar(50) NOT_NULL The name of the payment method used for imports from the finance controller. Used for import of open amounts, sales order or purchase orders. Example "PayPal" 
PaymentDefDO paymentDefRef integer The payment method the name of the finance controller should be used for.
